"jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-3S2","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":14904,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/suhur-recite-fifty-ayat\/","url_meta":{"origin":14882,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Prolonging pre-fasting meal before Fajr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Thabit reported: We ate the pre-fasting meal\u00a0with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and then we stood for prayer. It was asked, \u201cHow long was it between the two calls to prayer?\u201d Zayd said, \u201cIt was time enough to recite fifty verses from the Quran.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14890,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/do-not-neglect-suhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":14882,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Suhoor: Do not neglect blessed pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Harith reported: A man among the companions entered upon the Prophet while he was eating the pre-fasting meal. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, it is a blessing that Allah has given you, so do not abandon it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2162 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15014,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/14\/suhoor-blessed-sip\/","url_meta":{"origin":14882,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Angels bless those who eat pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe pre-fasting meal is a blessed meal, so do not abandon it even if you only take a sip of water. Verily, Allah and His angels send blessings upon those who take the pre-fasting meal.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14885,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/come-to-blessed-suhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":14882,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Come to the blessed pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-'Irbad ibn Sariyah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, invited me to the pre-fasting meal\u00a0during Ramadan and he said, \u201cOnward to the blessed meal!\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2344 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0631\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0636\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062f\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650\u064a \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14887,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/must-eat-suhoor\/","url_meta":{"origin":14882,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Eat the blessed pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miqdam ibn Ma\u2019dikarib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou must take the pre-fasting meal, for it is a blessed meal.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2164 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0642\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u0650\u064a\u0643\u064e\u0631\u0650\u0628\u064e\u00a0\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u063a\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064f\u062d\u064f\u0648\u0631\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27669,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/17\/best-suhur-dates\/","url_meta":{"origin":14882,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Suhoor: Best pre-fasting morni